  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I've been thinking about your walks — how was your 20-minute reset today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It was nice, I got to hear birds and felt fresh. But I think I missed my phone for 5 minutes. 😅 By the way, I saw a new Bollywood movie last weekend — have you heard of it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it was nice — missing the phone a bit is totally normal. Birds and fresh air are a good start! What movie was it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It was \"Dunki\" — a Shah Rukh Khan movie. His acting is always so good. I didn't get bored at all. You know, I also been thinking about starting a new project. Maybe related to cricket app. What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said \"Dunki\" — Shah Rukh Khan is a great pick! Good choice. A cricket app sounds fun — what kind of features do you want to add first?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe a score tracker and team builder. But I not sure where to start. Also, I thinking of adding Hindi language support — many people play cricket but don't know English well. What you think?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said \"score tracker and team builder\" — that's a solid plan! Adding Hindi makes sense, more people can enjoy the app. Should we start with one feature first?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, maybe start with score tracker first. It's simple and useful. I can build more on it later. Also, I think adding a chat feature for users in future — but that maybe later. Thanks for the advice. I should get back to work now. Talk to you later! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said \"score tracker first\" — yes, that's a smart move! A chat feature sounds cool for later. Take your time with work — we can talk again soon. Have a good day!"
    }
  ],
